divs: Sighting DetailsI was attending a BBQ on the beach at Shelter Island in sandiego for a friend ofmine when we spotted these objects seemingly coming up from the sea to the west. The objects we traveling vertically for some time, then proceeded south, onefollowing the other. Total duration of the sighting was about two minutes. Ihave never before seen anything like this and felt compelled to report it tosomebody. There were about 15 of us who saw these two objects and none of usknew what to make of it. We were not drinking alcoholic beverages or any typeof drugs. Just soda and hotdogs. Thank you for your time
Summary: Two multi lighted shapes coming up from the sea
